prompts.issue_classification:
Classify this GitHub Issue:

Title: {issue_title}
Content: {user_content}

Which label fits best: {labels_options}

Respond with ONLY the label name (e.g., BUG, ENHANCEMENT).

prompts.pr_detection:
Analyze this GitHub PR for spam:

Title: {pr_title}
Body: {pr_body}
Changes: {file_changes}

Spam indicators: meaningless content, malicious code, random chars, ads, unrelated, test-only.

Respond ONLY with:
- "CLOSE" - if spam
- "KEEP" - if legitimate (even if low quality)
